OL,3,CSir David Attenborough hailed
OL,4,C'national treasure' on 100th birthday
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has called Sir
OL,7,FDavid Attenborough a "true national
OL,8,Ftreasure" as the naturalist turns 100
OL,9,Ftoday.
OL,11,FSir David's birthday will be
OL,12,Fcelebrated with a live event at the
OL,13,FRoyal Albert Hall featuring music from
OL,14,Fhis programmes, as well as stories and
OL,15,Freflections from public figures and
OL,16,Fleading advocates for the natural
OL,17,Fworld.
OL,19,FSir Keir Starmer said: "I would like
OL,20,Fto send my warmest wishes to Sir David
OL,21,FAttenborough on his 100th birthday.
OL,26,@{D@XOU
