OL,3,CSir David Attenborough hailed
OL,4,C'national treasure' on 100th birthday
OL,6,FAttenborough has been on our TV
OL,7,Fscreens for more than seven decades
OL,8,Fpresenting programmes such as Planet
OL,9,FEarth and The Blue Planet.
OL,11,FDavid's early life
OL,13,FBorn on May 8 1926, his interest in
OL,14,Fnature started as a child when he
OL,15,Fcollected fossils.
OL,17,FHe went on to gain a Natural Sciences
OL,18,Fdegree from Clare College, Cambridge,
OL,19,Fafter attending Wyggeston Grammar
OL,20,FSchool for Boys in Leicester.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
