PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1778234502
OL,3,CSir David Attenborough hailed
OL,4,C'national treasure' on 100th birthday
OL,6,FHe served in the Royal Navy from 1947
OL,7,Fto 1949 before joining the BBC but was
OL,8,Finitially discouraged from appearing
OL,9,Fon screen because his bosses thought
OL,10,Fhis teeth were too big.
OL,12,FDespite their dental misgivings, he
OL,13,Flaunched his Zoo Quest series in 1954.
OL,15,FNow arguably the world's most famous
OL,16,Fnaturalist, he has proved to be as
OL,17,Fbrave and imaginative as he is warm
OL,18,Fand conscientious.
OL,20,FHe also has over 40 plants and species
OL,21,Fnamed after him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
