PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1778234502
OL,3,CSir David Attenborough hailed
OL,4,C'national treasure' on 100th birthday
OL,6,FHe is the only person to win BAFTAS in
OL,7,Fblack and white, HD and 3D and
OL,8,Freceived a knighthood in 1985 granting
OL,9,Fhim the title of Sir David
OL,10,FAttenborough.
OL,12,FThe broadcaster has been inundated
OL,13,Fwith messages and well-wishes from
OL,14,Fenvironmental and animal charities and
OL,15,Fhas also had a "wise" bull named after
OL,16,Fhim by animal charity Peta to
OL,17,Fcelebrate his birthday.
OL,19,FThe bull, named Sir Attenbullock, was
OL,20,Famong the first rescued through Peta
OL,21,FIndia's Delhi mechanisation project.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@UO]
